<H3> <TI>   State of Emergency in Puno Provinces Extended </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    State of Emergency in Puno Provinces Extended </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY0206224094 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network in 
Spanish 1800 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY0206224094 </F>
<F P=104>  Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The state of emergency has been extended until 
August in the Provinces of Carabaya, Sandia, and (San Antonio de 
Cupina), Puno Department, on the request of the Armed Forces. 
  The purpose of the extension of the state of emergency, 
which 
includes the suspension of individual rights, is to assist the 
countersubversive operations being carried out by the Army in 
that part of the country. 

