Daily Report 
<DATE1>  5 Jun 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> CARIBBEAN </F>
<F P=101> Cuba </F>
<H3> <TI>   Robaina, Cuban Delegation Arrive in Qatar </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Robaina, Cuban Delegation Arrive in Qatar </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL0606003794 Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks in 
Spanish 0000 GMT 5 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL0606003794 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Tele Rebelde and Cuba Vision Networks </F>
