<H3> <TI>   Minister Links Competitiveness, Need for Scientists </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Minister Links Competitiveness, Need for Scientists </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL0406135894 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 2300 
GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL0406135894 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
